## New outputs (in `recreate_av_<stem>_plots/`, each `.png` + `.pkl.gz`)
- `recreate_gyro_bode.png` — magnitude (dB) + phase (deg) vs frequency: original, reconstructed,
  Butterworth-alone, notch-alone (+ candidate if present).
- `recreate_gyro_nichols.png` — gain-vs-phase, two panels (full + crossover zoom), same curve set.
- `recreate_filter_response.txt` — table of **dB loss + phase** (+ group delay, Δphase) at the
  frequencies of interest, for original vs reconstructed (+ candidate). This is the numeric
  companion to the Bode/Nichols.

